org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_AnalysisModel.SAM

Interface SaExecHost

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ComputingResource, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, GaExecHost, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ProcessingResource, Resource, Scheduler
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SaExecHostImpl

    public interface SaExecHost
extends GaExecHost
    A representation of the model object 'Sa Exec Host'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Is Sched
    • Sch Slack
    • Sched Utiliz
    • IS Rswitch T
    • IS Rprio Range

    See Also:
    SAMPackage.getSaExecHost()
